description:
Dane is a personal trainer and he is VERY confident about what he does.

"I'm the best," he said. "I can get results with anyone."

"Yes," he said. "I have a lot of long-time clients. Some pretty amazing transformations!"

He also wasn't shy about showing off his body. He's got an amazing chest with a little bit of fuzz. He's is the epitome of the all-American boy!

He was shy about one thing, though... showing off his asshole!

"Why is that?" I asked him.

"I dunno," he replied. "I guess nobody has ever really seen my asshole before... I don't even think I've ever seen it. I'm kinda unsure of what it looks like."

Well, that's something to explore, for sure!

He also has a little daughter.

"So I guess that makes you a 'DILF' then, right?"

"What's a 'DILF'?" he asked...
title: Dane
